{"id":"5e5fac91a622ec0017745b22","title":"antd 4系にマイグレート","image":null,"created":1583328401,"updated":1583331774,"lines":[{"id":"5e5fac91a622ec0017745b22","text":"antd 4系にマイグレート","created":1583328401,"updated":1583328401},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d0000185264","text":"from [20200226] #0226","created":1583328402,"updated":1583331774},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d0000185265","text":"[antd] 4系にマイグレート","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d0000185266","text":"\t結構前にやったんだけどメモるのを忘れていた","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d0000185267","text":"\t基本的には https://next.ant.design/docs/react/migration-v4 をみればよい","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d0000185268","text":"\t\t使ってる範囲で主にやったのは `dropdownMatchSelectWidth` は `boolean` じゃなくて `number` になったっぽい","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d0000185269","text":"\t\t`TimePicker` の `defaultOpenValue` は `defaultValue` になった","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d000018526a","text":"\t\t\tmoment と dayjs の話が書いてあって、置き換えないといけないのかとおもったけど moment で十分そう","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d000018526b","text":"\t\t`Icon` まわりがごっそり変わって `@ant-design/icons` から import してくるようになった","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d000018526c","text":"\t\t`Table` が `ColumnProps` から `ColumnsType` に変わった","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d000018526d","text":"\t\t細かいけど `autosize` が `autoSize` に変わった","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d000018526e","text":"\t今のところ問題なくいけてる","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402},{"id":"5e5fac934ade4d000018526f","text":"\t\tちなみに、同じタイミングで yarn を berry にしようとしたんだけどこの antd まわりのパッケージの解決にどうしても失敗するので1系に戻した","created":1583328402,"updated":1583328402}]}